                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-118-victim883 t18180114-118-viclabel633"></join>. On the 11th of December, the bar at the shop-door fell down, the shirts were hanging at the door, I ran out and stopped the prisoner with the shirt - He three it down.</p>
               <p>HENRY JAY. I saw the prisoner take the shirt, and saw him drop it.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>WILLIAM BOND. I took the prisoner into custody; the bar on which the shirts hung was cut away.</p>
